=================
 Base Repository
=================

Synopsis:

A registry publishes a repository instance for each descriptor registered (should it use config admin?)

Usage:

Register a repository descriptor for each required repository instance. A corresponding repository will be registered as a service once initialised.

Services:
• Jcrom
• Session (?)

Dependencies:

• Sling embedded Jackrabbit
• Sling JCR API
• springmodules-jcr (?)
• jcrom

